message.content: The paper "Semi Supervised Question Retrieval With Gated Convolutions" belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and semantic representation of questions. Other likely sub-categories could be "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval), "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence), "cs.LG" (Machine Learning), and "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as these fields are closely related to the topic of the paper.
